Output docs/screenshot-05-cell-styles.png

Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set FontSize 13
Set Framerate 15
Set Padding 16
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"

Hide
Type `nvim --cmd "set rtp+=." samples/eval-demo.fsx`
Enter
Sleep 3s
Show

Escape
Type "gg"
Sleep 500ms
Type ":SageFsCellStyle full"
Enter
Sleep 1s
